# Formspree — one-time setup (free): https://formspree.io
# 1. Create a form and set the notification email to: irakozekelly41@gmail.com
# 2. Copy your form ID from the Formspree URL (e.g. https://formspree.io/f/abcxyz → abcxyz)
# 3. Copy this file to .env.local and paste your form ID below
# 4. Restart the dev server

NEXT_PUBLIC_FORMSPREE_FORM_ID=your_formspree_form_id_here
